---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Innovative Bubble Developer & No-Code Technologist with 5+ years enabling organizations and startups to rapidly validate, launch, and scale digital ideas. Specializes in building complex SaaS products, marketplaces, dashboards, and automations using Bubble. Recognized for creative problem solving, workflow automation, system integrations, and team mentorship in the no-code space.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Certified Bubble Developer"
      subtitle="Bubble.io Advanced Bootcamp, 2020"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="No-Code Workflow & API Automation"
      subtitle="Zeroqode Labs, 2019"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="B.E. Computer Engineering"
      subtitle="Gujarat Technological University, 2014–2018"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Senior Bubble Developer / Technical Consultant"
      subtitle="Freelance & Remote, 2019 – Present"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Designed and delivered 30+ Bubble applications: SaaS (ClientFlow CRM), analytics dashboards (Insightlytics), B2B platforms (MarketNest), internal business tools.</li>
        <li>Led end-to-end MVP launches, covering UI/UX, data architecture, workflow logic, and integrations with Stripe, Zapier, and custom APIs.</li>
        <li>Conducted regular performance tuning, app audits, and training workshops for client teams and juniors.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bubble Coach & Community Mentor"
      subtitle="Online Programs, 2021 – Present"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Mentored 100+ founders and developers on advanced Bubble strategies, performance, secure database design, and scalable workflows.</li>
        <li>Produced curriculum for self-paced learning: API, advanced conditions, plugin management, responsive UI.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Open Source Contributor – Bubble Tools"
      subtitle="Bubble.io Forum & GitHub, 2018 – Present"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4">
        <li>Shared 40+ how-tos, custom components, and reusable widgets with the Bubble community.</li>
        <li>Active in forum Q&A and collaborative Bubble development challenges.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      <a href="https://bubble.io/agency-directory" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Verified Bubble Professional Partner</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/bubble-visual-programming/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Udemy: Bubble App Builder Mastery</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.nocode.tech/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NoCode Accelerator Graduate</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>Bubble workflows & conditionals</li>
    <li>Advanced UI/UX in Bubble</li>
    <li>API Connector & backend workflows</li>
    <li>Marketplace & SaaS app architecture</li>
    <li>Stripe/PayPal integration</li>
    <li>External REST API integration</li>
    <li>Database privacy & security</li>
    <li>No-code automation (Zapier, Make)</li>
    <li>Reusable components & plugins</li>
    <li>Performance optimization</li>
    <li>Testing & QA on Bubble</li>
    <li>Open source Bubble development</li>
    <li>Mentoring developers & founders</li>
    <li>Agile and iterative product launch</li>
    <li>Custom analytics dashboards</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>